Angel Prime/Starwind/Steed/Lucky/Rattrap/Cheetor




Angel Prime sensors said the CF was under attack and he opened a com to all 
maximals.


Angel Prime:


"the CF is under attack all maximals support the defenders."





Starwing transformed into spaceship mode and rattrap,lucky,Steed all got in. 
Angel Prime flew next to Starwind as they flew toward the CF.



~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Cheetor took off across the land as he heard Angel Primes com.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~



Angel Prime flew above the battle at the CF and open a com to the attackers.



Angel Prime:




"this is Angel Prime you are out numbered retreat or die."


Lucky leaped out of Starwind as he was flying and gaining speed in his Troll 
form he pulled out his club and slammed it toward Soundwaves head.
